# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Prior to CMake 3.10 the CMake FindMPI module considers:
#   1. Inspect MPI wrappers (MPI_<lang>_COMPILER)
#   2. Try guesses
#   3. Try the compiler (CMAKE_<lang>_COMPILER)
#
# Starting with CMake 3.10 the CMake FindMPI module considers:
